": [{"indices": [161, 166], "text": "ONDS"}, {"indices": [167, 171], "text": "SPG"}], "symbols": [{"indices": [177, 182], "text": "AAOI"}, {"indices": [183, 188], "text": "RKLB"}], "timestamps": [], "urls": [], "user_mentions": [{"id_str": "17228511", "indices": [40, 56], "name": "Marcus Trent", "screen_name": "VeronicaManzAlb"}]}, "quoted_tweet": null, "retweeted_tweet": null, "isLimitedReply": false, "communityInfo": null, "article": null}}, {"reason": "cashtags=19", "tweet": {"type": "tweet", "id": "2050505052154966202", "url": "https://x.com/MMMTwealth/status/2050505052154966202", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/MMMTwealth/status/2050505052154966202", "text": "I assume you're looking for a stock in the space thematic that isn't trading at +10x sales (or more). \n\n-> $ASTS is at 117x sales \n-> $RKLB is at 52x sales\n\nFrequency Electronics | $FEIM\n\nNo satellites, no missiles, no GPS, no military communications - it's just the invisible layer that makes all of it work. \n\nThe only public competitor to $FEIM's atomic clocks is $MCHP which trades at 10x sales with negligible growth compared to $FEIM.\n\nWith $FEIM set to hit ~$150M in revenue by FY29, you're looking at a company growing +32% CAGR over the next 3 years. \n\nThat's just slightly less growth than a company like $RKLB that trades at 52x sales. \n\nObviously, I'm not comparing $RKLB to $FEIM. That'd be an idiotic comparison. $RKLB's TAM is infinite compared to $FEIM's niche market. \n\nBut you do have two high growth space companies trading at VERY different multiples. \n\nEven given $FEIM a 50% discount to a company like $RKLB and you're looking at a $3.75B company (vs $566M today). \n\nOr you can think of it this way. $RBC is a precision engineering component play for robotics. Yet you have $RBC trading at 10x sales with growth rates ~1/3rd of $FEIM's whilst $FEIM trades at 7x sales. \n\nI think at bare minimum $FEIM deserves ~12x multiple over time given their moat in this space and their growth. \n\n12x on $150M = $1.8B (2.5x from today). \n\nThis is a high growth component play in the space thematic. \n\nI bought before yesterday's 15% move. Admittedly lucky timing.", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 2, "replyCount": 2, "likeCount": 35, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 4012, "createdAt": "Sat May 02 09:17:55 +0000 2026", "lang": "en", "bookmarkCount": 44, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2050505052154966202", "displayTextRange": [0, 282], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "MMMTwealth", "url": "https://x.com/MMMTwealth", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/MMMTwealth", "id": "1630283681284669445", "name": "Oliver | MMMT Wealth (CPA)", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1726901308580364288/ZRQ_B4Mj_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1630283681284669445/1751011091", "description": "", "location": "Join 20,000+ members \ud83d\udc49", "followers": 65766, "following": 1039, "status": "", "canDm": true, "canMediaTag": true, "createdAt": "Mon Feb 27 19:08:31 +0000 2023", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 39033, "hasCustomTimelines": true, "isTranslator": false, "mediaCount": 2834, "statusesCount": 22143, "withheldInCountries": [], "affiliatesHighlightedLabel": {}, "possiblySensitive": false, "pinnedTweetIds": ["2029671544495149321"], "profile_bio": {"description": "Technical/Fundamental analyst, CPA, Owner of https://t.co/hO3l50hhRd, For my spreadsheet, watchlist, portfolio, daily notes, and live buys/sells/adds/trims \ud83d\udc47", "entities": {"description": {"urls": [{"display_url": "mmmtwealth.com", "expanded_url": "http://www.mmmtwealth.com", "indices": [45, 68], "url": "https://t.co/hO3l50hhRd"}]}, "url": {"urls": [{"display_url": "mmmtwealth.com", "expanded_url": "http://www.mmmtw